        "subject": "LU-2311 mdd: clean up orphan code style",
        "message": "LU-2311 mdd: clean up orphan code style\n\nRename externally-visible \"orph_*\" functions to \"mdd_orphan_*\":\n    orph_index_{name,init,fini} -> mdd_orphan_index_{name, init,fini}\n    orph_declare_index_insert ()-> mdd_orphan_declare_index_insert()\n    orph_declare_index_delete() -> mdd_orphan_declare_index_delete()\nRemove extraneous \"__\" prefix from mdd_orphan_{add,del,cleanup}()\nRemove extraneous function wrappers and call underlying code directly:\n    __mdd_orphan_{add,del,cleanup}()\n    mdd_orphan_{insert,delete}_obj()\n    mdd_orphan_ref_{add,del}()\nRemove unnecessary \"rc\" and \"is_dir\" variables in mdd_finish_unlink()\nFix tab indenting around any modified code.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I8314116347dd10c6984f87fc63cbca8a38500c1e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
